Usage
=====
important
---------
<esc> is unmaped in input mode, instead 'jk' comb. is used. Aimed to force your hand stay on central keyboard.

fast configuration
------------------
fast edit: ,e
fast source .vimrc: auto after save

Install
===========
To activate the configuration files, use
$bash install.sh

insall.sh:
#!/bin/bash
mv ~/.vimrc ~/.vimrc.bak
mv ~/.vim ~/.vim.bak
ln -s `pwd`/vimrc ~/.vimrc 
ln -s `pwd`/vim ~/.vim
